queries.text:
_capacityBase
| where ['Sku'] in (_capacityType)
| count

let workspaces_count = _capacityOperationsNoFilter
    | summarize Workspaces=count_distinct(['Workspace Id']) by ['Capacity Id'];
_capacitySummaryNoFilter
| where ['Capacity Sku'] in (_capacityType)
| project
    ['Consumption %'],
    ['Capacity Id'],
    ['Capacity Name'],
    ['SKU'] = ['Capacity Sku'],
    ['Window Start Time'],
    ['Interactive Delay Threshold %'],
    ['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'],
    ['Background Rejection Threshold %']
| summarize
    arg_max(['Window Start Time'], ['Consumption %'],['Interactive Delay Threshold %'], ['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'], ['Background Rejection Threshold %'], ['SKU'])
    by ['Capacity Id'], ['Capacity Name']
| extend ['Capacity Usage %'] = round(['Consumption %'], 2)
| extend  ['Capacity Usage %'] = iff(isnan(['Capacity Usage %']), 0.0, ['Capacity Usage %']),
    ['Int Delay %'] = iff(isnan(['Interactive Delay Threshold %']), 0.0, round(['Interactive Delay Threshold %'],2)),
    ['Int Rejection %'] = iff(isnan(['Interactive Rejection Threshold %']), 0.0, round(['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'],2)),
    ['Back Rejection %'] = iff(isnan(['Background Rejection Threshold %']), 0.0, round(['Background Rejection Threshold %'],2))
| lookup workspaces_count on ['Capacity Id']
| lookup _capacityLastSate on $left.['Capacity Id'] == $right.capacityId
| project
    ['Capacity Name'],
    ['Capacity Id'],
    ['SKU'],
    Workspaces,
    ['Capacity Usage %'],    
    ['Int Delay %'],
    ['Int Rejection %'],
    ['Back Rejection %'],
    ["Capacity State"]=iff(isempty(capacityState), "Active", capacityState),
    ["State Change Reason"]=stateChangeReason
| where Workspaces > 0
// | order by ['Capacity Name'] asc
| order by ['Capacity Usage %'] desc

_capacitySummary
| summarize ['Interactive CU´s']=sum(['Interactive CU´s']), ['Background CU´s']=sum(['Background CU´s']), ['Interactive Preview CU´s']=sum(['Interactive Preview CU´s']), ['Background Preview CU´s']=sum(['Background Preview CU´s']) by  ['Capacity Id'], ['Capacity Name']

_capacitySummary
| summarize ['Interactive CU´s']=sum(['Interactive CU´s']), ['Background CU´s']=sum(['Background CU´s']), ['Interactive Preview CU´s']=sum(['Interactive Preview CU´s']), ['Background Preview CU´s']=sum(['Background Preview CU´s']), ['Timepoint Base CU']=sum(['Timepoint Base CU'])
| project ['Interactive CU´s %']=100*['Interactive CU´s']/['Timepoint Base CU'],['Background CU´s %']=100*['Background CU´s']/['Timepoint Base CU'],['Interactive Preview CU´s']=100*['Interactive Preview CU´s']/['Timepoint Base CU'],['Background Preview CU´s']=100*['Background Preview CU´s']/['Timepoint Base CU']
| evaluate narrow()
| project Column, Value=toreal(Value)

let _timespan = case(
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(730d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(365d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(60d), timespan(6h),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(14d), timespan(1h),
    _endTime - _startTime > timespan(1d), timespan(30m),
    timespan(30s)
);
_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'],*) by ['Window Start Time'],['Capacity Id']
| project ['Overage CU´s'],['Overage Add CU´s'],['Overage Burndown CU´s']=-['Overage Burndown CU´s'], ['Capacity Id'], ['Capacity Name'], ['Window Start Time']

_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'], ['CU´s'], ['Timepoint Base CU'])
| project iff(isnan(['CU´s']),0.0,round(100*['CU´s']/['Timepoint Base CU'],2))

_capacityOperationsFilterWS
| project ['Item Id']
| summarize Workspaces=count_distinct(['Item Id'])

let _timespan = case(
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(730d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(365d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(60d), timespan(6h),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(14d), timespan(1h),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(2d), timespan(1m),
    timespan(30s)
);
_capacityOperationsFilterWS
| extend ['CU´s']=['CU´s'], ['Capacity Name'], ['Time']
| make-series ['CU´s']=sum(['CU´s']) on ['Time'] step _timespan by ['Capacity Name'], ['Utilization Type']

_capacityOperationsFilterWS
| summarize round(sum(['CU´s']),2)

_capacityOperationsFilterWS
| count

let _timespan = case(
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(730d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(365d), timespan(1d),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(60d), timespan(6h),
    _endTime - _startTime >= timespan(14d), timespan(1h),
    _endTime - _startTime > timespan(1d), timespan(30m),
    timespan(30s)
);
_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'],*) by ['Window Start Time'],['Capacity Id']
| project ['Interactive Delay Threshold %'], ['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'], ['Background Rejection Threshold %'], ['Capacity Id'], ['Capacity Name'], ['Window Start Time']

let _capacityState = CapacityState | where transitionTime between (_startTime .. _endTime);
_capacityBase
| where CapacityId in (_capacities)
| lookup _capacityState on $left.CapacityId ==  $right.capacityId
| project ["Capacity State"]=iff(isempty(capacityState),"Active",capacityState), transitionTime,Sku, stateChangeReason
| summarize arg_max(transitionTime,['Capacity State'], stateChangeReason,Sku)
| project ['Capacity State'] = iff(['Capacity State'] == "Active",['Capacity State'],stateChangeReason)

_capacityBase
| where CapacityId in (_capacities)
| lookup CapacityState on $left.CapacityId ==  $right.capacityId
| project ["Capacity State"]=iff(isempty( capacityState),"Active",capacityState), transitionTime,Sku
| summarize arg_max(transitionTime,['Capacity State'],Sku)

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity=_capacities,
    Workspace=_workspaceNameExact,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=true,
    AddPreview=true
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Item Name'], ['Item Id'], ['Item Kind'], ['Operation Name'], ['Releast Type'],['Consumed Timepoint CU']=round(['Consumed Timepoint CU']), ['% of Capacity']
| order by ['% of Capacity']

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=false,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Workspace Name'],['Workspace Id'], ['Consumed Timepoint CU']=round(['Consumed Timepoint CU'],2), ['% of Capacity']=round(['% of Capacity'],2)
| order by ['% of Capacity']

TimepointFutureConsumption(
    Capacity = _capacities,
    Timepoint = bin(_endTime-30s,30s)
) 
| extend ['% of Capacity Units'] = iff(['% of Capacity Units']>100,100.0, ['% of Capacity Units'])

_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'],['Interactive Delay Threshold %'])
| project iff(isnan(['Interactive Delay Threshold %']),0.0,round(['Interactive Delay Threshold %'],2))

_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'],['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'])
| project iff(isnan(['Interactive Rejection Threshold %']),0.0,round(['Interactive Rejection Threshold %'],2))

_capacitySummary
| summarize arg_max(['Window Start Time'],['Background Rejection Threshold %'])
| project iff(isnan(['Background Rejection Threshold %']),0.0,round(['Background Rejection Threshold %'],2))

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime - 30s, 30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=false,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id'] == $right.CapacityId
| project
    ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName,
    Sku,
    ['Workspace Name'],
    ['Workspace Id'],
    ['Consumed Timepoint CU']=round(['Consumed Timepoint CU'], 2),
    ['% of Capacity']=round(iff(isempty(['% of Capacity']), 0.0, ['% of Capacity']), 2),
    ['Item Kind']
| order by ['% of Capacity']

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Workspace=_workspaceNameExact,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=true,
    AddPreview=true
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Item Name'], ['Item Id'], ['Item Kind'], ['Operation Name'], ['Releast Type'],['Consumed Timepoint CU'], ['% of Capacity']
| top 10 by ['Consumed Timepoint CU']
| project ['Consumed Timepoint CU'], ['Item Name']

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Workspace=_workspaceNameExact,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=true,
    AddPreview=true
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Item Name'], ['Item Id'], ['Item Kind'], ['Operation Name'], ['Releast Type'],['Consumed Timepoint CU'], ['% of Capacity']
| top 10 by ['% of Capacity']
| summarize  ['% of Capacity'] = sum(['% of Capacity']) by ['Item Kind']

_capacityLastSate
| where capacityState == "Overloaded"
| summarize Count=count()
| project State=iff(Count > 0, "Overloaded", "Ok")

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Workspace=_workspaceNameExact,
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=false,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=true
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Item Name'], ['Item Id'], ['Item Kind'], ['Operation Name'], ['Releast Type'],['Consumed Timepoint CU'], ['% of Capacity']
| top 10 by ['Consumed Timepoint CU']
| project ['% of Capacity']

TimepointFutureConsumption(
    Capacity = _capacities,
    Timepoint = bin(_endTime-30s,30s)
) 
| where ['% of Overage Capacity Units'] == 0
| summarize arg_min(['Window Time'], ['% of Overage Capacity Units'])
| project ['Window Time'] = ['Window Time'] - 9m - 30s

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    ItemKind="SynapseNotebook",
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Workspace Name'],['Workspace Id'], ['Item Name'], ['Item Kind'], ['Consumed Timepoint CU']=round(['Consumed Timepoint CU'],2), ['% of Capacity']=round(['% of Capacity'],2)
| where ['% of Capacity'] > 0.5
| order by ['% of Capacity']
| project ['% of Capacity'], ['Item Name'] = strcat(['Workspace Name']," - ", ['Item Name'])

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    ItemKind="SynapseNotebook",
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=false,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.['Capacity Id']== $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name']=CapacityName, Sku, ['Workspace Name'],['Workspace Id'], ['Consumed Timepoint CU']=round(['Consumed Timepoint CU'],2), ['% of Capacity']=round(['% of Capacity'],2)
| order by ['% of Capacity']

let _capacityState = CapacityState | where transitionTime between (_startTime .. _endTime);
_capacityBase
| where CapacityId in (_capacities)
| lookup _capacityState on $left.CapacityId ==  $right.capacityId
| project ["Capacity State"]=iff(isempty( capacityState),"Active",capacityState), transitionTime,Sku
| summarize arg_max(transitionTime,['Capacity State'],Sku)

_capacityBase
| where CapacityId in (_capacities)
| lookup CapacityState on $left.CapacityId ==  $right.capacityId
| project ["Capacity State"]=iff(isempty( capacityState),"Active",capacityState), transitionTime,Sku
| summarize arg_max(transitionTime,['Capacity State'],Sku)

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    ItemKind="SynapseNotebook",
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| distinct ['Workspace Name'], ['Item Name']
| count

TimepointConsumption(
    Timepoint=bin(_endTime-30s,30s),
    Capacity= _capacities,
    ItemKind="SynapseNotebook",
    AddWorkspace=true,
    AddItem=true,
    AddOperation=false,
    AddPreview=false
)
| where ['% of Capacity'] > 0.5
| distinct ['Workspace Name'], ['Item Name']
| count

_capacityOperations
| where  ['Item Kind'] == "SynapseNotebook"
| distinct ['Workspace Name'], ['Item Name']
| count

CapacitySummary
| where windowStartTime between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| lookup _capacityBase on  $left.capacityId ==  $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Id'] = capacityId,
['Capacity Name'] = CapacityName,
['Capacity Sku'] = capacitySku,
['CU´s'] = capacityUnitMs/1000.0,
['Consumption %'] = 100*(capacityUnitMs/1000.0)/timepointCapacityUnits,
['Window Start Time'] = windowStartTime,
['Window End Time'] = windowEndTime,
['Timepoint Base CU']=timepointCapacityUnits,
['Base CU']=baseCapacityUnits,
['Interactive CU´s']=utilizationInteractive/1000.0,
['Background CU´s']=utilizationBackground/1000.0,
['Interactive Preview CU´s']=utilizationInteractivePreview/1000.0,
['Background Preview CU´s']=utilizationBackgroundPreview/1000.0,
['Overage CU´s']=overageTotalCuMs/1000.0,
['Overage Add CU´s']=overageAddCuMs/1000.0,
['Overage Burndown CU´s']=overageBurndownCuMs/1000.0,
['Interactive Delay Threshold %']=interactiveDelayThresholdPercentage,
['Interactive Rejection Threshold %']=interactiveRejectionThresholdPercentage,
['Background Rejection Threshold %']=backgroundRejectionThresholdPercentage

CapacityOperations
| where ['time'] between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| lookup _capacityBase on $left.capacityId == $right.CapacityId
| project ['Capacity Name'] = CapacityName,
['Capacity Id'] = capacityId,
['Capacity Sku'] =capacitySku,
['Workspace Name'] = workspaceName,
['Workspace Id'] = workspaceId,
['CU´s'] = capacityUnitMs/1000.0,
['Domain'] = workspaceDomain,
['Domain Id'] = workspaceDomainId,
['Parent Domain'] = workspaceParentDomain,
['Parent Domain Id'] = workspaceParentDomainId,
['Window Start Time'] = windowStartTime,
['Window End Time'] = windowEndTime,
['Time']=['time'],
['Operation Name'] = operationName,
['Item Name'] = itemName,
['Item Id'] = itemId,
['Item Kind'] = itemKind,
['Timepoints'] = (windowEndTime - windowStartTime) /30s,
['Timepoint CU'] = (capacityUnitMs/1000.0)/((windowEndTime - windowStartTime)/30s),
['Utilization Type']=utilizationType,
['Operation Start Time'] = operationStartTime,
['Duration Ms'] = durationMs

_capacityOperations
| where ['Workspace Id'] in (_workspaceNameExact)
| where ['Item Id'] in (_item)

_capacitySummaryNoFilter
| where ['Capacity Id'] in (_capacities)

_capacityOperationsNoFilter
| where ['Capacity Id'] in (_capacities)

CapacityState
| where transitionTime <= _endTime
| summarize arg_max(transitionTime,capacityState,stateChangeReason) by capacityId

CapacitySummary
| distinct capacitySku

_capacityBase
| where ['Sku'] in (_capacityType)
| project CapacityId, CapacityName

CapacityOperations
| where ['time'] between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where workspaceName contains _workspaceNameSearch
| where capacityId in (_capacities)
| distinct workspaceId,workspaceName
| take 1000

CapacityOperations
| where windowStartTime  between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where capacityId in (_capacities)
| where workspaceId in (_workspaceNameExact)
| project 
['Workspace Id'] = workspaceId,
['Operation Name'] = operationName,
['Item Name'] = itemName,
['Item Id'] = itemId,
['Item Kind'] = itemKind
| summarize by ['Item Id'], ['Item'] = strcat(['Item Name']," - ", ['Item Kind']), ['Workspace Id']
